targets.rawSql:
SELECT 
  title 
FROM channel 
WHERE id='$channelId'

SELECT 
  id AS "ID",
  title AS "Title"
FROM channel 
WHERE id='$channelId'

SELECT 
  "videosPublished" AS "Videos"
FROM channel 
WHERE 
  id='$channelId'

SELECT 
  COUNT(DISTINCT "categoryId") AS "Categories" 
FROM video 
WHERE video."channelId"='$channelId'

SELECT 
  SUM("viewCount") as "Views",
  SUM(likes) as "Likes",
  SUM(dislikes) as "Dislikes",
  SUM("commentCount") as "Comments"
FROM video
WHERE "channelId"='$channelId'

SELECT 
  EXTRACT(YEAR FROM "publishedAt") AS "Year",
  COUNT(*) AS "Videos Published"
FROM video
WHERE "channelId"='$channelId'
GROUP BY "Year"
ORDER BY "Year"  DESC

SELECT 
  max_freq,
  category.title
FROM into_values((SELECT mcv_agg(1, "categoryId") FROM video WHERE "channelId"='$channelId')) AS values
JOIN category ON category.id = values.value
ORDER BY max_freq DESC
LIMIT 3

WITH most AS 
  (
    SELECT
      video."categoryId",
      SUM("viewCount") AS "Views"
    FROM video
    WHERE "channelId"='$channelId'
    GROUP BY video."categoryId"
    ORDER BY SUM("viewCount") DESC
    LIMIT 3
  )
SELECT 
  category.title AS "Category",
  most."Views"
FROM 
  category, most
WHERE 
  category.id = most."categoryId"
ORDER BY most."Views" DESC

WITH most AS 
  (
    SELECT
      video.title AS "Video Title", 
      video."channelId",
      video."categoryId" AS "Category",
      MAX("viewCount") AS "Views"
    FROM
      video
    WHERE video."channelId"='$channelId'
    GROUP BY video.id
    ORDER BY MAX("viewCount") DESC
    LIMIT 3
  )
SELECT 
  most."Video Title", 
  channel.title AS "Channel", 
  most."channelId" AS "Channel ID",
  category.title AS "Category",
  most."Views"
FROM 
  channel, most, category
WHERE 
  channel.id = most."channelId" 
  AND category.id = most."Category"
ORDER BY most."Views" DESC

WITH most AS 
  (
    SELECT
      video.title AS "Video Title", 
      MAX(likes) AS "Likes",
      video."channelId",
      video."categoryId" AS "Category"
    FROM
      video
    WHERE video."channelId"='$channelId'
    GROUP BY video.id
    ORDER BY MAX(likes) DESC
    LIMIT 3
  )
SELECT 
  most."Video Title", 
  channel.title AS "Channel", 
  most."channelId" AS "Channel ID",
  category.title AS "Category",
  most."Likes"
FROM 
  channel, most, category
WHERE 
  channel.id = most."channelId" 
  AND category.id = most."Category"
ORDER BY most."Likes" DESC

WITH most AS 
  (
    SELECT
      video.title AS "Video Title", 
      MAX(dislikes) AS "Dislikes",
      video."channelId",
      video."categoryId" AS "Category"
    FROM
      video
    WHERE video."channelId"='$channelId'
    GROUP BY video.id
    ORDER BY MAX(dislikes) DESC
    LIMIT 3
  )
SELECT 
  most."Video Title", 
  channel.title AS "Channel", 
  most."channelId" AS "Channel ID",
  category.title AS "Category",
  most."Dislikes"
FROM 
  channel, most, category
WHERE 
  channel.id = most."channelId" 
  AND category.id = most."Category"
ORDER BY most."Dislikes" DESC

WITH most AS 
  (
    SELECT
      video.title AS "Video Title", 
      MAX("commentCount") AS "Comments",
      video."channelId",
      video."categoryId" AS "Category"
    FROM
      video
    WHERE video."channelId"='$channelId'
    GROUP BY video.id
    ORDER BY MAX("commentCount") DESC
    LIMIT 3
  )
SELECT 
  most."Video Title", 
  channel.title AS "Channel", 
  most."channelId" AS "Channel ID",
  category.title AS "Category",
  most."Comments"
FROM 
  channel, most, category
WHERE 
  channel.id = most."channelId" 
  AND category.id = most."Category"
ORDER BY most."Comments" DESC

SELECT 
  COUNT(*) AS "Videos Published"
FROM video
WHERE 
  EXTRACT(YEAR FROM "publishedAt") = $year
  AND "channelId"='$channelId'

SELECT
  COUNT(*) AS "Trends"
FROM trend
WHERE 
  "channelId"='$channelId' 
  AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM "trendingDate" AT TIME ZONE 'UTC') = $year

WITH most AS 
  (
    SELECT
      "videoId",
      COUNT(*) AS "Trends"
    FROM trend
    WHERE 
      "channelId"='$channelId' 
      AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM "trendingDate" AT TIME ZONE 'UTC') = $year
    GROUP BY "videoId"
    ORDER BY "Trends" DESC
    LIMIT 10
  )
SELECT 
  video.title AS "Video",
  most."Trends"
FROM 
  video, most
WHERE 
  video.id = most."videoId"
ORDER BY "Trends" DESC

SELECT  
  title AS "Video Title",
  EXTRACT(YEAR FROM "publishedAt" AT TIME ZONE 'UTC') AS "Year",
  id AS "Video ID"
FROM video
WHERE
  EXTRACT(YEAR FROM "publishedAt" AT TIME ZONE 'UTC') = $year
  AND "channelId" = '$channelId'
ORDER BY "publishedAt" DESC
